{"tid":953476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=？工作壓力爆煲　華荔邨80後燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-12-24T03:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T05:27:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9018aa6f76cb4cbac73fd5c592817d622f8e21","tid":953476,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"周一（24日）平安夜清晨6時許，一名32歲姓潘的男子被父親揭發於長沙灣華荔邨賞荔樓住所睡房內燒炭，不省人事。救護員趕抵證實男事主已明顯死亡，毋須送院。警方在場檢獲遺書，<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉事主受工作問題困擾</span>，不排除他因此尋死，將案件列作「自殺」處理，並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，事主與父母同住上址，事發時其父母起床後聞到炭味，心感不妙進入兒子睡房查看，即見事主用兩個盤燒炭，可惜為時已晚，兩老於佳節當前痛失愛子，事後情緒十分激動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/274692/疑工作壓力爆煲-華荔邨男子燒炭亡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F274692%2F%E7%96%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2-%E8%8F%AF%E8%8D%94%E9%82%A8%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD%E4%BA%A1&d=shPZLtxq8zKrM9oTtNKLMVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=46ff1188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/274692/疑工作壓力爆煲-華荔邨男子燒炭亡</a>"},{"pid":"46a095072fa5e5ef205910f8fbc4eecbc11abeb4","tid":953476,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204a62abfa0d4eb8cffe116e03375ee0800389a4","tid":953476,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"80 後一味做做做， 到頭來又係同父母住公屋， 過節對住工作同父母<br />\n<br />\n幾多80後係同一情況 ..."},{"pid":"d042f19588f44fb64b98fedba9f0a40decee130d","tid":953476,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:05:32.000Z","msg":"公屋仔 打份狗工搵得雞碎咁多 俾左家用扣埋必要洗費都冇乜得淨 而家先quit game算遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5ec83ec921135c19e7f6ba7860706fa6571dc2","tid":953476,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:06:09.000Z","msg":"3x仲要同佬母住都幾灰<img src=